  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nDesktop issue for https://github.com/status-im/status-go/issues/4230\r\n\r\n> We will need to develop a mechanism to retrieve shard information for a given community ID. One idea is to use a pubsub topic where the control node can publicly announce the shard information.\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\n- Without prior knowledge of the community (new install for example), the app is able to get the community description and display it, from just the community ID, whether the community is sharded or not.\r\n\r\n",
